":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5a283ee72dca403226408e517017fc4ad51948a","tid":867232,"uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b222704152500d5ae1424ae209e99712335a226e","tid":867232,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"PCCW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"不過我覺得Habbitzz聰明在定位高檔啲，利潤高啲可以負擔到運送成本<br />\n賣水賣米係就係單多，但係利潤低加運送成本貴，好多單都要蝕錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"個名咁特別應該同世界杯時賣廣告個間一樣,<br />\n唔駛你D平民用我,食有錢人中產個水就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38a26a515a266bd2b170267b253ba124eae1946","tid":867232,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0e79744fa32f816b5e797a826f3d0345f17b8b","tid":867232,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5a283ee72dca403226408e517017fc4ad51948a","tid":867232,"uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b222704152500d5ae1424ae209e99712335a226e","tid":867232,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"PCCW <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"不過我覺得Habbitzz聰明在定位高檔啲，利潤高啲可以負擔到運送成本<br />\n賣水賣米係就係單多，但係利潤低加運送成本貴，好多單都要蝕錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"個名咁特別應該同世界杯時賣廣告個間一樣,<br />\n唔駛你D平民用我,食有錢人中產個水就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"Habbitzz一名使用了雙字母，很可能是方便搜索引擎優化，同時也是&ldquo;leetspeak&rdquo;的一個例子。這個詞是網絡術語，指將單詞中的某些字母用語音或可視的元素替代。但該網站本身主打高端、高品質商品，因此採用這一名稱策略似乎有些奇怪。但leetspeak最初也是一種黑客的&ldquo;精英&rdquo;語言形式，因此它可能仍然適用於Habbitzz的高端定位。 <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們只是想脫離habit一詞的常規拼寫，從而讓我們的名字更難忘、更特別。特別是habit這個詞對消費者來說有點平淡，&rdquo;電訊盈科解釋道。"},{"pid":"14a718f78c538600e4d08a9b9a7d7ac39bbf3642","tid":867232,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"得手機app無web client<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全部賣luxury野,電子野一定貴過amazon買水貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3085ae4ab552ee96a1b39fe2aa9edd9a220ea2","tid":867232,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d38a26a515a266bd2b170267b253ba124eae1946","tid":867232,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0e79744fa32f816b5e797a826f3d0345f17b8b","tid":867232,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5a283ee72dca403226408e517017fc4ad51948a","tid":867232,"uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"不過我覺得Habbitzz聰明在定位高檔啲，利潤高啲可以負擔到運送成本<br />\n賣水賣米係就係單多，但係利潤低加運送成本貴，好多單都要蝕錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"個名咁特別應該同世界杯時賣廣告個間一樣,<br />\n唔駛你D平民用我,食有錢人中產個水就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk